<item>
            <title>[LU-11404] improve fsync() and fdatasync()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11404</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;workload like dd oflag=sync causes MDS_SYNC RPC on every write(2) syscall.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;given the only things we store on MDS are file itself and layout it should be enough to send MDS_SYNC once (to sync file creation) and once for every layout change.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
